M||tx|"When the us wants help w/ paid advertising cg on Google ad, Meta (Facebook/Instagram), LinkedIn, Twitter/X, or other ad platforms. Also use when the us mentions 'PPC,' 'paid media,' 'ROAS,' 'CPA,' 'ad cg,' 'retargeting,' 'audience targeting,' 'Google ad,' 'Facebook ad,' 'LinkedIn ad,' 'ad budget,' 'cost per click,' 'ad spend,' or 'shd I run ad.' Use this for cg st, audience targeting, bidding, and op. For bulk ad creative generation and iteration, see ad-creative. For landing page op, see page-cro."
