M|3. A|it|What problem does your pd solve for them?
M|3. A|it|What are they searching for or interested in?
M|3. A|it|Do you have existing cs data for lookalikes?
M|4. C|it|Have you run ad before? What worked/didn't?
M|4. C|it|Do you have existing px/conversion data?
M|4. C|it|What's your current funnel conversion rate?
